Something strange in a country where the king officially has 14 wives.
The last absolute monarch of Black Africa, King Mswati III, is known for his opulent lifestyle and fraught with excesses.
Polygamy instead of democracy.
This officially unaccepted way of life is largely responsible for the spread so fast that the HIV virus has experienced in recent decades.
